    #faq

      %h2
        Frequently Asked Questions
      .faq
        .question
          How many links or buttons can I put on my website?
        .answer
          As many as you want.
      .faq
        .question
          Why do I need to integrate MadBooker with my Google Analytics account?
        .answer
          You don't have to. As long as you add the MadBooker buttons or link to your site, the booking engine will work.
          %br
          %br
          Linking MadBooker with your Google Analytics account enables you to see some additional reports, in the Reports section, about who is visiting your website (Visits, Citites, and Sources). Statistics regarding your booking engine will be provided in the Reports section whether or now you link up with Google Analytics.

          
        
        
        
